Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:45.72,Default - Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Com'è potuto succedere?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,È stata annegata.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:51.19,Default - Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Non possiamo esserne certi\N senza un'accurata analisi,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(640,0)\p1shad0\bord0\fscx500\fscy600\c&H913618&\1a&H59&\blur1\pos(212.05,260.746)}m -14 -3 l 15 -3 l 15 7 l -14 7
